results.name: Theta series for 10-dimensional 4-modular lattice Q10 with minimal norm 4.
comment: If there were a 10-dimensional unimodular lattice with minimal norm 2, this would also be its theta series; however, no such lattice exists.
reference: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. 416.
